Schema validation failed:

Entities missing the @storage directive (multi-storage mode requires it):
  - Apple
  - Mango
  - Zebra

Fixes:
  - Add @storage(postgres: true) and/or @storage(clickhouse: true) to the entities listed above. Example:
      type Apple @storage(postgres: true) { ... }
      type Apple @storage(clickhouse: true) { ... }
